description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint a secretary / administrator to support the service manager and senior leadership team across the OPMH / LD portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whilst this role is primarily supporting the leadership team there will be a requirement to support all staff in achieving compliance with internal performance indicators.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will require the successful candidate to be flexible in their approach, along with a good sense of humour and the ability to problem solve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Krissie Sadler-Brough, Operational Service Line Manager - OPMH / LDl ,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;kristina.sadler-brough@nhs.net, 01246 515559&lt;/p&gt;
